OL,5,GThe recent renewal of the channel 3
OL,6,Gregional licences highlights an
OL,7,Gimportant historic anomaly.
OL,9,FIn a purely legal sense, there are
OL,10,Fstill two separate ITV licences
OL,11,Fcovering London.
OL,13,FA London weekday licence runs from
OL,14,F9.25am on Monday to 5.15pm on Friday `
OL,15,Fapart, of course, from the breakfast
OL,16,Fhours.
OL,18,FThen, in licensing terms at least, the
OL,19,Friverfolk on the South Bank take over
OL,20,Fso you have "a good London Weekend".
