OL,5,FOf course, this is a simple historic
OL,6,Fanachronism.
OL,8,FTechnical handovers ended in 1993 when
OL,9,FCarlton London and LWT started to
OL,10,Fshare playout facilities. The two
OL,11,Fcompanies also worked together to
OL,12,Fcreate a coherent 7-day news operation
OL,13,Ffor the first time.
OL,15,FThe on-screen distinction between the
OL,16,Ftwo London licences ended in 2002 when
OL,17,Fnetwork continuity was introduced.
OL,19,FLWT ` lately part of Granada ` has
OL,20,Flong been killed off by ITV plc.
