OL,3,CITV London split lives on
OL,5,FAnd no separate programme obligations
OL,6,Fexist for the London Weekend licence.
OL,7,FThe regional news commitments are
OL,8,Fdelivered across the week in
OL,9,Fconjunction with the weekday licence.
OL,11,FYou might be tempted to think that
OL,12,Fmerging the two licences into one ITV
OL,13,FLondon licence would be an obvious bit
OL,14,Fof housekeeping.
OL,16,FThis, presumably, would be no
OL,17,Fdifferent to the separation of Wales
OL,18,Ffrom the West of England and the
OL,19,Fcreation of a single licence covering
OL,20,Fboth the former HTV West and
OL,21,FWestcountry areas.
