OL,5,FIt would not be dogged by the
OL,6,Fpotential difficulties which prevent a
OL,7,Flicence covering all of Scotland from
OL,8,Fbeing created.
OL,10,FSo why not do it?
OL,12,FThere is still one meaningful
OL,13,Fdistinction between the two London
OL,14,Flicences.
OL,16,FUndertakings on advertising sales were
OL,17,Fgiven at the time ITV plc was created
OL,18,F20 years ago.
