OL,5,FEssentially this means that
OL,6,Fadvertising in the London region on
OL,7,Fweekdays is sold separately from
OL,8,Fadvertising at the weekends.
OL,10,FThis explains the one on-screen
OL,11,Fdifference which remains: the local
OL,12,Fweather at the weekend has a different
OL,13,Fsponsor.
OL,15,FI can never quite decide if the
OL,16,Fvoiceover says "ITV London ` weekend
OL,17,Fweather" or "ITV London Weekend
OL,18,Fweather".
OL,20,FOf course, all those licensing quirks
OL,21,Fare a reminder of another time.
