OL,3,CITV London split lives on
OL,5,FProbably nobody under 30 who isn't a
OL,6,Fstudent of broadcasting will know that
OL,7,FLondon once had two separate ITV
OL,8,Fcompanies.
OL,10,FAnd nobody much under 40 will know
OL,11,Fthat Thames and LWT were not always
OL,12,Fthe best of chums.
OL,14,FJust like the 9.25am handover between
OL,15,Fbreakfast and the regions though,
OL,16,Fsomething which was once significant
OL,17,Fstill exists in a very specific sense
OL,18,Fbehind the scenes.
